ll, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1015427, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O my God! I made it to the evening as one who cannot attain what he hopes to attain and cannot fend off what he dislikes except by You I made it to the evening while I am responsible for my own actions I made it to the evening with my destiny in Your Hand O Lord! There is no poor one poorer than me Please bestow Your Blessings on Muhammad and his Progeny.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA INNEE AM-SAIY-TO LAA AMLE-KO MAA ARJOO WA LAA AS-TATEE-O’ DAF-A’ MAA O-HAAZE-RO ILLAA BEKA WA AM-SAIY-TO MURTA-HANAN BE-A’MA-LEE WA AM-SAL AMRO WAL QAZAA-O BE-YADE-KA YAA RABBE FALAA FAQEE-RA AF-QARO MINNEE FA-SALLE A’LAA MOHAMMADIW WA AALE MOHAMMADIN.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ اِنِّيْ اَمْسَيْتُ لَا اَمْلِكُ مَا اَرْجُوْ وَلَا اَسْتَطِيْعُ دَفْعَ مَا اُحَاذِرُ اِلَّا بِكَ وَاَمْسَيْتُ مُرْتَهَنًا بِعَمَلِيْ وَاَمْسَى الْاَمْرُ وَالْقَضَاءُ بِيَدِكَ يَا رَبِّ فَلَا فَقِيْرَ اَفْقَرُ مِنِّيْ فَصَلِّ عَلٰى مُحَمَّدٍ وَّآلِ مُحَمَّدٍ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign