fter during this great month without any hardship for me And do not destroy my soul and body seeking what is not destined for me by Your Mercy O the Most Compassionate, Most Merciful.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": "WAGH-FIR-LEE YAA RABBE ZULMEE WA JURMEE WA JAHLEE WA JIDDEE WA HAZLEE WA KULLA ZAMBIR TAKAB-TOHU WA BALLIGH-NEE WAR-ZUQNEE KHAI-RAD DUNYAA WAL AAKHE-RATE FEE HAA-ZASH SHAH-RIL A’ZEEME FEE GHAIRE MASHAQ-QATIN MINNEE WA LAA TOHLIK ROOHEE WA JASA-DEE FEE TALABE MAA LAM TO-QADDIR LEE BE-RAH-MATEKA YAA AR-HAMAR RAAHE-MEENA.", "ArabicText1": "وَاغْفِرْ لِيْ يَا رَبِّ ظُلْمِيْ وَجُرْمِيْ وَجَهْلِيْ‌ وَجِدِّيْ وَهَزْلِيْ وَكُلَّ ذَنْۢبٍ ارْتَكَبْتُهٗ وَبَلِّغْنِيْ وَارْزُقْنِيْ خَيْرَ الدُّنْيَا وَالْآخِرَةِ فِيْ هٰذَا الشَّهْرِ الْعَظِيْمِ فِيْ غَيْرِ مَشَقَّةٍ مِنِّيْ وَلَا تُهْلِكْ رُوحِيْ وَجَسَدِيْ فِيْ طَلَبِ مَا لَمْ تُقَدِّرْ لِيْ بِرَحْمَتِكَ يَا اَرْحَمَ الرَّاحِمِيْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicTex